# Dependency Management Guide

## Core Libraries
- Jetpack Compose: 1.5.0 or higher
- Kotlin: 1.9.0 or higher
- Coroutines: 1.7.0 or higher
- Hilt: 2.48 or higher

## Version Management
- Use Version Catalog
- Manage with libs.versions.toml
- Regular dependency updates required
- Compatibility testing mandatory

## Module Dependencies
- No circular dependencies
- Use Hilt for dependency injection
- Test dependencies in testImplementation
- Debug dependencies in debugImplementation

## Security
- Follow ProGuard/R8 rules
- Manage sensitive info in BuildConfig
- Network security configuration required
- Apply latest security patches
